## Enumerations

### enum class  {#a9ebf832762357f1668dbc7fd07668de4}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype="enum class llvm::WebAssembly::BlockType : unsigned"
 labels = {["strong"]}>
Used as immediate MachineOperands for block signatures.

<EnumerationList title="Enumeration values">

<Link id="a9ebf832762357f1668dbc7fd07668de4a4bbb8f967da6d1a610596d7257179c2b" />
<EnumerationListItem name="Invalid">
